title: Various Artists - Navigatorz Fresh!! Indie Playlist Best Of 2011
description:
Welcome to one of special edition for this year, of NAVIGATORZ FRESH!! Indie playlists... you'll be able to download two more special NAVIGATORZ playlists - NAVIGATORZ FRESH!! BEST INDIE REMIXES OF 2011, and THE BEST INDIE COVERS OF 2011... Anyone who is interested in sending your own stuff (via links to downloads) for indie playlist in 2012, we would gladly listen to your music and include it in our list or radio show if we find it good, so more people would hear it...This month artwork is from Bojan Saptovic & Mia Matovic. 

Best regards

Navigatorz team

P.S. of course, if you like the music, support the artists and buy their music!

NAVIGATOR, music team producing beats,grooves and much more...And an awesome DJ team and a soundsystem as well proudly presents:

NAVIGATORZ FRESH!! INDIE PLAYLIST BEST OF 2011

NAVIGATORZ FRESH!! INDIE Playlist Best Of 2011 contains the team's choice when it comes to Indie, Soul, Electronic... versions of Indie songs. 

Enjoy!
